I found myself dropping the SAM Api in favor of `AWS::ApiGateway::RestApi` (which meant adding Stage/Deployment too) so I could include the full swagger body in the CF template. Now I'm able to avoid the `stageVariables` altogether because I can grab the ARN of the lambda functions in places like `x-amazon-apigateway-authorizer`. In my `AWS::Serverless::Function` Events, I just point to the RestApi instead of the SAM Api and that seems to work.

